@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jtsesu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.19)) / ((v0 + 0.48 + v0 + 0.92) * tmp))
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.70) * (v1 + 0.46 - tmp + 0.94)))
    v1 = 0.39
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v1 + 0.65 / v0 + 0.63)))
    v1 = 0.47
    tmp = ((v0 * (tmp + 0.68 * tmp + 0.23)) + wp.exp(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
